WorkMarket,is,a,labor,resource,platform,that,can,be,used,to,find,professionals,get,assignments,or,both,The,service,enables,companies,to,engage,find,verify,pay,manage,and,rate,the,employees,that,work,for,them,The,WorkMarket,API,allows,integration,with,outside,platforms,and,messaging,services,and,also,enables,large,data,transfers,For,full,documentation,contact,the,WorkForce,sales,team